---
import RetroGrid from './RetroGrid.astro';
---

<section id="nosotros" class="bg-dark py-20 relative">
  <RetroGrid glowPosition="bottom-left" />
  
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 relative z-10">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4 font-mono neon-text">¿QUIÉNES SOMOS?</h2>
      <div class="w-24 h-1 bg-neon-purple mx-auto glow-effect"></div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <div class="retro-card transform hover:scale-105 transition duration-300" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
        <div class="absolute -top-3 -left-3 w-6 h-6 border border-neon-purple opacity-70"></div>
        <div class="absolute -bottom-3 -right-3 w-6 h-6 border border-neon-purple opacity-70"></div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 font-mono neon-text-purple">NUESTRA ESENCIA</h3>
        <p>Transformia es el aliado que traduce tus desafíos en oportunidades de crecimiento digital.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="retro-card transform hover:scale-105 transition duration-300" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
        <div class="absolute -top-3 -left-3 w-6 h-6 border border-neon-blue opacity-70"></div>
        <div class="absolute -bottom-3 -right-3 w-6 h-6 border border-neon-blue opacity-70"></div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 font-mono neon-text-blue">NUESTRA INSPIRACIÓN</h3>
        <p>Innovamos constantemente buscando soluciones que generen valor real para nuestros clientes.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="retro-card transform hover:scale-105 transition duration-300" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="300">
        <div class="absolute -top-3 -left-3 w-6 h-6 border border-neon-pink opacity-70"></div>
        <div class="absolute -bottom-3 -right-3 w-6 h-6 border border-neon-pink opacity-70"></div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 font-mono neon-text-pink">NUESTRA MOTIVACIÓN</h3>
        <p>Impulsamos la transformación digital para hacer más eficientes y rentables tus procesos.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Elemento decorativo -->
    <div class="mt-20 flex justify-center relative">
      <div class="absolute w-64 h-64 bg-neon-purple opacity-5 rounded-full blur-[50px] animate-pulse-slow"></div>
      <div class="p-6 retro-card max-w-2xl text-center">
        <blockquote class="text-xl italic mb-4">
          "La innovación distingue a los líderes de los seguidores."
        </blockquote>
        <p class="font-mono">— Steve Jobs</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .retro-card {
    position: relative;
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
  }
  
  @keyframes pulse-slow {
    0%, 100% {
      opacity: 0.05;
      transform: scale(1);
    }
    50% {
      opacity: 0.1;
      transform: scale(1.1);
    }
  }
</style>